NUMBER 2303
NAME Shaft, really wide part
DEEPCAVE
DARKNESS
EXIT ABOVE 2302
EXIT BELOW 2304
DROPLOC 2304

IFVAR FLYING ! 1
        IFVAR RAC ! 8
                ECHO PLAYER You're starting to get the hang of this falling-to-your-death business.
                ECHO OTHERS %N falls to the cave floor below.
                DISBAND
                EQUAL INTNUM60 444
                MOVE 2304
                AFFECT 2304
                ECHO OTHERS %N comes shooting down from above, smashing into the cave floor, bouncing off one wall and coming to rest in bad shape.
        ENDIF
