NUMBER 2307
NAME Stone passage
DEEPCAVE
DARKNESS

*DESCRIPTION_START
You make your way through the passage, moving between roughened walls of
ancient, hardened lava and smoother, more recent formations. Light shines in
a steady, but uselessly dim glow from below while above you is only darkness.
*DESCRIPTION_END

