*DESCRIPTION_START ITEM READ 0
In shaky script you read, "Rhadthys- if you read this, know that I am looking
for the temple of Nuthruk below. I do not expect to die, but such things have
happened to others better-prepared than myself. If you feel the need to come
after me, the platform below is magical. If it is not there, speak the words
"Notho Tather Tolu" to bring it up to your location. When standing on it, you
can say the same thing to make it rise to the top, if it is not there, or
say "Tather Tolu Sthare" to make it descend. It will go where it is supposed
to. It can be stopped at any time with the word, "Slothes". I do not know who
built it, but when I return I hope to. Of course, if you ever read this I will
be long dead..." The lines of writing are signed with a simple "G" rune.
*DESCRIPTION_END

