NAME Temple of the Goblin Gods
DEEPCAVE
FIXED_LIGHT

*DESCRIPTION_START
The interior of the building is much simpler than you would have expected
from a temple. One side of it is lined in sand with a few drying splotches
of blood worked into it by the passage of goblin feet. The other side is
simply a garbage pit, laden with the cores and rinds of various fruits and
any number of animal bones and skins.
*DESCRIPTION_END

